INSERT INTO `pages` VALUES (3,'Home','home','','homepage','home','light','',0,1,'0','','Balcones Resources is a comprehensive environmental services company. We\r\n specialize in recovering resources through traditional <a target=\"\" title=\"\" href=\"/balcones-recycling/balcones-recycling\">recycling</a>, \r\n<a target=\"\" title=\"\" href=\"/balcones-shred/balcones-shred\">document destruction</a> and <a target=\"\" title=\"\" href=\"/alternative-energy/alternative-energy\">alternative energy</a>. Balcones is not associated \r\nwith a landfill, which makes us experts in diverting recyclable \r\nmaterials away from your trash bin and into our recycling program.<br><br>Since\r\n 1994, Balcones has created customized recycling programs for hundreds \r\nof businesses in the Austin, Dallas-Fort Worth and Little Rock \r\nmetropolitan areas. Each customer has its own set of challenges and \r\ngoals. We\'re here to help you maximize the effectiveness of your \r\nrecycling, including helping you with office recycling for <a target=\"\" title=\"\" href=\"/balcones-recycling/commercial/leed-assistance\">LEED#REG# \r\ncertification</a>.<br><br>Working with Balcones Resources is a partnership. \r\nWe offer janitorial training, employee awareness events, marketing \r\nmaterials and reporting, all geared toward increasing your recycling \r\nefforts. Your participation is rewarded through generous rebates and \r\ndecreased landfill costs.<br><br>Not sure where to start? Request a Resource Audit, and we\'ll guide you the rest the of way.&nbsp; <br><br>','Block 2 Content','Block 3 Content','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','Simply More Resourceful','Block 2 Title','Block 3 Title','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'plastic recycling dallas, city of austin recycling, commercial recycling austin, recycle austin, single stream recycling austin, aluminum recycling austin, austin recycled paper, plastic recycling austin, glass recycling austin, cardboard recycling austin, little rock recycling, plastic recycling little rock, cardboard recycling little rock, commercial recycling little rock','Balcones Resources provides commercial recycling services for offices in DFW, Austin and Little Rock areas. We are a primary leader in waste management by recycling paper, plastic, aluminum, and cardboard.<br>','Balcones | Recycling &amp; Document Destruction for Dallas, Austin, &amp; Little Rock<br>',1),(22,'Mills & Reprocessors','mills-and-reprocessors','','millsandbrokers','millsandbrokers','','34',900,0,'2','','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'recycling austin, cardboard recycling dallas, paper recycling austin, austin waste management, dallas waste management, dallas recycled paper, plastic recycling dallas, balconesresources.com, commercial recycling dallas, commercial recycling austin','Learn how Balcones Resources benefits mills and reprocessors through its Dallas and Austin paper recycling services.','Balcones Resources | Recycling Austin, Cardboard Recycling Dallas, Paper Recycling Austin',1),(12,'Recycling','balcones-recycling','','none','internal-green','','23',100,0,'1','','Balcones Resources was founded on recycling and has grown to become the largest independent recycler in the Southwest. Our first recycling programs were designed for the commercial printing industry. Since then we’ve developed customized recycling programs for a host of industries and businesses including multi-tenant buildings, manufacturing facilities, distribution centers and corporate campuses.<br><br>We are not associated with a landfill, so we only accept materials that we can responsibly recycle. Balcones recycles several grades of paper, plastic, metal and glass*.&nbsp;Our <a target=\"\" title=\"\" href=\"/balcones-recycling/commercial/single-cycle\">SingleCycle#REG#</a> program makes recycling easy for participants. SingleCycle#REG# takes the guesswork out of recycling and allows users to comingle all acceptable items in a single recycling container. Sorting is no longer necessary.<br><br><i>*Austin market only</i><br><br>','We work diligently with our <a target=\"\" title=\"\" href=\"/balcones-recycling/commercial\">commercial and office recycling</a> customers to\r\n find the best solution tailored to their needs without fabricating \r\nnumbers or making empty promises. Diverting recyclables from landfills \r\nnot only benefits the environment, it also helps our customers’ bottom \r\nline. Through decreased landfill costs and revenue sharing, our \r\nstakeholders quickly see an impact. Partner with us and become a \r\nresponsible steward for the environment and your budget.&nbsp; <br><br>Interested\r\n in a recycling program for your business? Check out our <a target=\"\" title=\"\" href=\"/balcones-recycling/commercial/services\">list of \r\nservices</a> and request a complimentary <a target=\"\" title=\"Resource Audit\" href=\"http://balconesresources.com/Resource-Audit\">Resource Audit</a> to get you started.','Balcones Resources is proud to be a partner with the City of Austin\'s Resource Recovery team.&nbsp; We currently receive 60% of the city\'s residential recycling.&nbsp; If you are interested in learning more about how we are helping Austin achieve its Zero Waste plan, please visit the <a target=\"\" title=\"\" href=\"http://www.balconesresources.com/balcones-recycling/residential\">Residential</a> section of our website.&nbsp; <br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','Zero Waste','Commercial Recycling - Austin, Dallas, Little Rock','Residential Recycling - Austin Market','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'single stream secycling, computer recycling, paper recycling, aluminum recycling, recycle electronics, commercial recycling, commercial recycling, recycle, city of dallas, austin, and little rock','Recycling for your home or company will pay you to help the environment. Balcones Resources offers residential &amp; commercial recycling services to families and businesses alike. We have our recycling facilities in Dallas, Austin, &amp; Little Rock.','Balcones | Commercial Recycling Center, Dallas, Austin, &amp; Little Rock',1),(13,'Shred','balcones-shred','','none','internal-purple','','27',200,0,'1','','Balcones Shred is a trusted and secure commercial document destruction provider with locations in Austin and the Dallas–Fort Worth Metroplex. We provide the gamut of document destruction services, from shredding to e-waste destruction.<br><br>Balcones Shred is big enough to meet all of our customers’ service needs and small enough to offer personalized care. From two-person offices to multi-site businesses, we help our commercial shredding customers remain industry and government compliant.<br><br>For more information about Balcones Shred, please visit our website at <a target=\\\"\\\" title=\\\"Balcones Shred Website\\\" href=\\\"http://www.balconesshred.com\\\">www.balconesshred.com</a>.<br>','We pick up your material and bring it back to our secure facility for shredding.','One of our mobile shredding trucks comes to your location, and we shred your material in your presence.','Weekly, biweekly or monthly shredding.','For periodic cleanouts with occasional, biannual or onetime shredding service.<br>','We help secure products not intended for the public through destruction before disposal. <br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','Destroying for Good#TM#','Off-site shredding','On-site shredding','Scheduled/recurring service','Purge service','Product destruction','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'Commercial recycling austin, commercial recycling dallas, dallas waste management, recycle austin, cardboard recycling dallas, cardboard recycling austin, alumnimun recycling austin, plastic recycling austin, URO, Austin waste management','In addition to providing Austin and Dallas commercial recycling services, Balcones Resources has added commercial document destruction services in Dallas.','Balcones Resources | Commercial Recycling Austin, Commercial Recycling Dallas, Paper Recycling Dallas',1),(14,'Alternative Energy','alternative-energy','','none','internal-red','','28',300,0,'1','','Balcones Resources Fuel Technology was created to help achieve our goal of zero waste. Our fuel technology plant located in Little Rock, Arkansas, takes items that cannot be traditionally recycled, diverts them from the landfill, and transforms them into alternative energy. Our patented process takes these waste items and converts them into fuel cubes.&nbsp;Fuel cubes are used as an alternative energy source in facilities that would traditionally use coal in their boilers or need a quality wood fuel replacement.<br><br>Our alternative energy plant is a landfill alternative which extends the life of disposable items and gives companies a boost to their diversion rates.&nbsp; <br><br>Balcones Resources pushes sustainability to the next level as we continue to look for creative solutions for zero waste. Is your material a candidate for our fuel technology process? <a target=\\\"\\\" title=\\\"\\\" href=\\\"/contact-us/\\\">Contact us</a> today for more information.<br><br>','Balcones fuel cubes are an alternative, cost-effective energy which produces high BTU levels while burning cleaner than coal or wood.<br><br>These small cubes pack a punch. Measuring only 1’\\\' x 2”, their unique composition of clean manufacturing by-products offer the following advantages:&nbsp; <br><ul><li>Substantially higher BTU values when compared to conventional fuels, such as wood</li></ul><ul><li>Consistent moisture levels, BTU values, purity and quality</li></ul><ul><li>Competitive prices with wood fuel on a cost-per-BTU basis</li></ul><ul><li>Stable pricing, regardless of an unstable market</li></ul><ul><li>Reduced transportation and handling costs</li></ul><ul><li>Compatibility with most fuel feed systems</li></ul><ul><li>An economical and practical alternative to landfilling clean manufacturing by-products</li></ul><br>Our fuel cubes are made from 60% non-chlorinated petroleum derivatives and 40% cellulosic fibers from wood pulp. The average range of BTUs per pound is 12,400 to 13,500.<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','Engineered for Energy','About','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'Recycling Little Rock, balconesresources.com, recycling austin, cardboard recycling austin, recycling schedule austin, computer recycling austin, electronic recycling dallas, recycle austin, glass recycling austin, city of austin recycle','<div>Learn more about our Little Rock and Austin recycling services.</div>','Balcones Resources | Recycling Little Rock, Dallas Waste Management, Recycling Austin',1),(15,'How + Why','how-why','','none','internal-yellow','','29',400,0,'1','','<div><div>Why are certain materials accepted in my residential program but not in my commercial program? What happens to all of the items after I’ve done my part? Should I wash my aluminum cans and plastic bottles?</div><div><br></div><div>There is a method to the madness. Let us answer your questions about recycling and sustainability. We want to be a resource to you and help you understand your recycling program, our process and why it all matters.</div><div><br></div><div>The idea that drives Balcones Resources is simple: Don’t waste resources that can be used again. Whether you call it conservation, preservation, reuse or recycling, it’s common sense. Balcones believes in extracting the maximum amount of value from all recyclable commodities. The actual recycling process varies depending on the material, but the general idea is the same. Explore the links below to learn the nitty-gritty facts about recycling.</div></div><div>\r\n\r\n<!--EndFragment--></div>','<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <o:DocumentProperties>\r\n  <o:Revision>0</o:Revision>\r\n  <o:TotalTime>0</o:Total