ost of the PP plastic we receive ends up as flower pots.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border:none;mso-padding-alt:31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt;\r\nmso-border-shadow:yes\">Buying products made from post-consumer recycled content\r\ncloses the loop and creates demand for recovered resources. Remember living sustainably doesn’t end with\r\nrecycling.&nbsp; Purchasing these types of products is an important part of the equation.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border:none;mso-padding-alt:31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt;\r\nmso-border-shadow:yes\">Learn more about the reincarnation of recyclables here: <a target=\"_blank\" title=\"What do they become?\" href=\"http://iwanttoberecycled.org/learn\">www.iwanttoberecycled.org/learn</a>.<br></p>','<code></code><code><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/a-KF4kSGuVM\" ;=\"\" allowfullscree=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"268\" width=\"476\"></iframe><br></code><font size=\"1\">This PSA was filmed on location at M&amp;T Bank Stadium, which is home to \r\nthe NFL’s Baltimore Ravens. The stadium’s exterior, and additional \r\nselect areas throughout the venue, is constructed partially from \r\npost-consumer recycled aluminum.</font><br><h5><code></code></h5>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','Transforming your Throwaways','What Does it Become?','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'cardboard recycling austin, boxboard recycling austin, plastic recycling dallas, aluminum recycling austin, aluminum recycling dallas, glass recycling austin, commercial recycling dallas, recycle electronics dallas, dallas waste management, cardboard recycling little rock, plastic recycling little rock, commercial recycling little rock, recycling little rock','What does it become? Balcones transforms Austin cardboard recycling, Little Rock paper recycling, and Dallas plastic recycling into its original form and back in the market for reuse.','Balcones Resources | Cardboard Recycling Austin, Plastic Recycling