ing and computer recycling solutions that are vertically integrated, closed loop and 100% green compliant</li></ul><ul><li>Minimized risk with certified and secure destruction, including data destruction, with no downstream partners to manage</li></ul><ul><li>With&nbsp;four electronic recycling centers and more than 754,000 square feet, ROUND2 is one of the largest electronics recyclers in the Central U.S.</li></ul><ul><li>R2 and ISO certifications allow ROUND2 to maximize recovery value while minimizing environmental concerns<br></li></ul><br>For more information about ROUND2, visit <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" title=\\\"\\\" href=\\\"http://www.round2.net\\\">www.round2.net</a>.<br>','Our partnership with Goodwill Industries of Central Texas allows both companies to explore new business opportunities while making recycling more accessible to the general public in Austin and San Antonio. Balcones Recycling will assist Goodwill Industries in their paper, plastic and glass recycling efforts. This means the non-profit will become a licensee of Balcones’ SingleCycle#REG# program and will be qualified to help smaller businesses that cannot hold a standard size Balcones dumpster to recycle.<br><br>Goodwill Industries of Central Texas is a non-profit 501(c)3 organization dedicated to the mission of generating lifelong connections to work. Revenue generated through the sale of donated goods is used to fund job training and employment programs for Central Texans. For more information about Goodwill Industries of Central Texas, go to <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" title=\\\"\\\" href=\\\"http://www.austingoodwill.org\\\">www.austingoodwill.org</a>.<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','With a Little Help from Our Friends','ROUND2','Goodwill Industries of Central Texas','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'Electronic Recycling Dallas, Electronic Recycling Austin, Computer Recycling Dallas, ecoworks austin, dallas waste management','Balcones Resources h