paper recycling austin, austin waste management, dallas waste management, dallas recycled paper, plastic recycling dallas, balconesresources.com, commercial recycling dallas, commercial recycling austin','Balcones Resources has distringuished its self by partnering with Austin Waste Management and Dallas Waste Management teams. Balcones provides trusted commercial recycling to the Dallas area.','Balcones Resources | Austin Waste Management, Dallas Waste Management, Commercial Recycling Dallas',1),(52,'Process','process','','none','internal-red','','28',310,0,'3','','Balcones Resources patented Fuel Technology process creates sustainable sustainable alternative energy from materials like waxed cardboard or label matrix. Our process begins by salvaging these materials from the landfill and then transforming them into an alternative fuel suitable for a number of applications. The goal of our fuel cube process is to extend the life and add an additional use to materials which are not recyclable.','<ol><li>Material arrives via trucks or roll-off boxes.</li><li>Material is floor sorted to check for contaminants.</li><li>Material is then mixed into a recipe.</li><li>Next, it is pushed on the conveyor which moves it to a shredder.</li><li>Once it is shredded, the material is then transferred to a metering bin for further mixing.</li><li>After mixing, the material is run by a magnet to remove any metal.</li><li>Once the material is free of metal it is moved to the cuber where it is compressed into 1\\\" x 2\\\" cubes.</li><li>After it is cubed, the material is conveyed to semi trailers for delivery to our customers where they\\\'ll be used as a replacement fuel for coal or wood.</li></ol>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','Process','Step by Step Process ','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'Universal Recycling Ordinance Austin, Recycling Austin, URO Austin, URO Workshops Austin, plastic recycling austin, paper recycling austin, commercial recycling austin, residential recycling austin, austin waste management, URO','In addition to partnering with Austin waste management and Austin\\\'s URO, Balcones Resources in Little Rock creates sustainable alternative energy from waste.','Balcones Resources | Austin Waste Management, URO Austin, Dallas Waste Management',1),(50,'Collection Schedule','collection-schedule','','none','internal-green','','26',195,0,'3','','All residential recycling in the City of Austin is collected by the city. To view your collection schedule, <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" title=\\\"\\\" href=\\\"http://www.austintexas.gov/department/residential-curbside-collection-schedule\\\">click here</a> to go to the City of Austin’s Resource Recovery website.<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','Collection Schedule','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'City of Austin recycling, city of austin recycling, uro, austin recycling schedule, recycling austin, cardboard recycling austin, glass recycling austin, austin waste management, URO austin, computer recycling austin','The City of Austin recycling initiative includes URO education to the metro area. Check back for your updates to your Austin recycling schedule.','Balcones Resources | Recycling Schedule Austin, City of Austin Recycling, URO',1),(57,'Dallas','jobs-dallas','','none','internal-blue','','32',720,0,'3','','Currently there are no open positions at our Dallas location.&nbsp; <br><br>We are always on the lookout for good people.&nbsp; If you feel you would be a fit for Balcones Resources, <a target=\"\" title=\"\" href=\"mailto:careers@balconesresources.com\">send us</a> your resume, and we\'ll keep it on file for future positions.&nbsp; <br><br>Keep recycling!','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','Dallas Jobs','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'Commercial Recycling Dallas, Boxboard Recycling Austin, Glass Recycling Dallas, URO workshops, Dallas Waste Management, dallas recycled paper, electronics recycling dallas','Submit your resume and join the Balcones family as a member of our Dallas commercial recycling team.','Balcones Resources | Commercial Recycling Dallas, Electronics Recycling Dallas, Glass Recycling Dallas<br>',0),(51,'Wood','wood','','none','internal-green','','25',155,0,'3','','Pallets, especially broken pallets, can be a headache for facilities. If you’re in the central Arkansas area, wood recycling is a special service offered through our Balcones Fuel Technology plant in Little Rock. Pallets or lumber scraps can be delivered to our facility for recycling via compactors, open tops and trailers. We do <u>not</u> accept green wood, and all wood must be trash free and untreated.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br><br>The wood is chopped and any metal is separated. The wood is then sent to pressboard mills to be used in particleboard for construction. Alternatively, some of the wood is used as boiler fuel in manufacturing plants. <br><br>For more information on wood recycling, contact <a target=\\\"\\\" title=\\\"\\\" href=\\\"mailto:steves@balconesresources.com?subject=Wood%20Recycling%20Inquiry\\\">Copeland Hughes</a>, 501.490.0500.<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','Wood Recycling','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'Recycling little rock, recycle little rock, city of little rock recycling, balconesresources.com, commercial recycling dallas, commercial recycling austin, cardboard recycling dallas, cardboard recycling austin','Our Little Rock recycling plant will take your broken wood pallets and recycle them into resusable materials.','Balcones Resources | Recycling Little Rock, Recycle Little Rock, City of Little Rock Recycling',1),(53,'Fuel Feedstock','feedstock','','none','internal-red','','28',305,0,'3','','Zero waste is in sight with Balcones Fuel Technology.&nbsp; The process can take a variety of materials ordinarily destined for the landfill and gives them an additional use as an alternative fuel.&nbsp; <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>These are some of the wastes we routinely convert into fuel:<br><br><ul><li>Label Matrix</li></ul><ul><li>Software Destruction</li></ul><ul><li>Personal Care Products</li></ul><ul><li>Food Packaging Waste</li></ul><ul><li>MRF Residuals</li></ul><ul><li>Urban Wood and Pallets</li></ul><ul><li>Agricultural Waste</li></ul><ul><li>Waxed Cardboard</li></ul><br>If your company is struggling to find eco-friendly, feasible, sustainable alternatives to landfill dumping, <a target=\\\"\\\" title=\\\"\\\" href=\\\"/contact-us/contact-us\\\">contact us</a>.<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','Fuel Feedstock ','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'Plastic Recycling Austin, Paper Recycling Dallas, Cardboard Recycling Austin, plastic recycling dallas, recycled paper dallas, boxboard recycling austin, cardboard recycling dallas, commercial recycling dallas, recycling austin, glass recycling dallas','In addition to our recycling in Austin and plastic recycling in Dallas, Balcones in Little Rock converts waste into alternative fuel.','Balcones Resources | Recycling Austin, Plastic Recycling Dallas, Commercial Recycling Dallas',1),(54,'Fuel Users','end-users','','none','internal-red','','28',330,0,'3','','<div>Balcones Resources\\\' alternative fuel cubes are suitable for use at paper mills, lime and cement kilns, power plants, or any plant with wood-fired boilers.</div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>Balcones fuel cubes offer many advantages:<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br><ul><li>High consistent BTU values</li></ul><ul><li>Consistency in moisture levels, BTU values and quality</li></ul><ul><li>Competitive pricing</li></ul><ul><li>Stable pricing, regardless of the market</li></ul><ul><li>Engineered to work with most fuel feed systems</li></ul><ul><li>An answer to our National Energy Policy, which calls for alternative energy supplies to help diversify our nation’s energy portfolio</li></ul>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>If you feel your company could benefit from Balcones Resources alternative fuel technology,&nbsp;<a target=\\\"\\\" title=\\\"\\\" href=\\\"/contact-us/\\\">contact us</a> today.<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','Fuel Users ','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'Recycling Austin, Single Stream Recycling Austin, Computer recycling austin, paper recycling austin, aluminum recycling dallas, recycle electronics dallas, commercial recycling dallas, commercial recycling austin, recycle austin, little rock recycling','Balcones Resources provides aluminum recycling in Dallas, computer recycling in Austin and creates alternative energy fuel cubes.','Balcones Resources | Aluminum Recycling Dallas, Computer Recycling Austin, URO Workshops',1),(63,'Austin\\\'s Universal Recycling Ordinance','Austin-Universal-Recycling-Ordinance','','none','internal-green','','25',175,0,'3','','<span style=\\\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\" arial\\\",\\\"sans-serif\\\";=\\\"\\\" mso-fareast-font-family:calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#505050;=\\\"\\\" mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa\\\"=\\\"\\\"><br style=\\\"mso-special-character:line-break\\\">\r\n</span>','<span style=\\\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\">To\r\nmeet the requirements of the City of Austin’s Universal Recycling Ordinance (URO),\r\nwhich became effective October 1, 2012, affected<strong><span style=\\\"font-family:\r\n\\\"> multifamily and commercial office</span></strong> <strong><span style=\\\"font-family:\\\">property owners</span></strong> must\r\nsubmit an annual <a href=\\\"http://austinrecycles.us2.list-manage.com/track/click?u=67064d72d5ce19a53d3ae33d8&amp;id=8cff4b81d6&amp;e=da5f4fa39a\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#3B5998\\\">Recycling Plan form</span></a> to\r\nAustin Resource Recovery.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong><span style=\\\"font-family:\\\">Forms must be submitted\r\nby February 1, 2013.</span></strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\nMultifamily properties with more than 75 dwelling units and commercial\r\nproperties larger than 100,000 square feet must complete the Recycling Plan\r\nform:&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http://austinrecycles.us2.list-manage2.com/track/click?u=67064d72d5ce19a53d3ae33d8&amp;id=49d9737362&amp;e=da5f4fa39a\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#3B5998\\\">www.austintexas.gov/recyclingplan</span></a>.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\nFor questions about recycling, educating employees and tenants, or completing\r\nthe form, please contact <em><span style=\\\"font-family:\\\"><a href=\\\"mailto:commercialrecycling@austinrecycles.com?subject=Recycling%20Plan%20Form\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#3B5998\\\">CommercialRecycling@austinrecycles.com</span></a></span></em>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nFor more information about the Universal Recycling Ordinance, please visit: <a href=\\\"http://austinrecycles.us2.list-manage.com/track/click?u=67064d72d5ce19a53d3ae33d8&amp;id=4f13d65a25&amp;e=da5f4fa39a\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#3B5998\\\">www.austintexas.gov/commercialrecycling</span></a>.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;\r\n<br></span></span>','Are you confused by the requirements of the City of Austin\\\'s Universal Recycling Ordinance (URO)?&nbsp; Do you need help navigating the paper work and the reporting?&nbsp; Let Balcones help take you from confused to compliant.&nbsp; Attend one of our URO workshops.&nbsp; <br><br>The Balcones URO Workshop covers the following topics:<br><ul><li>Education</li><li>Labeling</li><li>Collection</li><li>Reporting<br></li></ul><br>Next workshop date is <b>Thursday, February 21, 2013</b> at <b>3pm</b> at Balcones Resources\\\' Corporate Headquarters located at <b>9301 Johnny Morris Road</b> in Austin.&nbsp; Food and drinks will be served.<br><br>Workshops are held on the last Thursday of each month.&nbsp; Future dates are:<br><br><div align=\\\"center\\\">March 28, 2013<br>April 25, 2013<br>May 30, 2013<br>June 27, 2013<br>July 25, 2013<br>August 29, 2013<br>September 26, 2013<br>October 31, 2013<br></div><br>No workshop will be held in November or December due to holiday scheduling conflicts.<br><br>Space is limited.&nbsp; To register for the Balcones URO Workshop, please email <a href=\\\"mailto:courtney@balconesresources.com?subject=URO Workshop\\\">Courtney Hannaford</a>.&nbsp; Please indicate your date of interest.<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','The URO','Austin\\\'s Universal Recycling Ordinance','URO Workshops','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'URO, Austin\\\'s universal recycling ordinance, balconesresources.com, uro workshops austin, single stream recycling austin, recycle austin, recycling austin, event recycling austin, residential recycling austin, singlecycle austin','URO, or Austin\\\'s Universal Recycling Ordinance, requires commercial companies to submit a recycling plan. Visit us for upcoming URO workshops in Austin.','Balcones Resources | URO, URO Austin, Austin Waste Management',0),(59,'Sustainability Scorecard','Resource-Audit','','contact','internal-blue','','33',810,0,'','','Let us conduct a FREE resource audit for your company.&nbsp; We\'ll assess the good, the bad and the ugly, and we\'ll prepare a report of our findings and a proposal to strengthen your program.&nbsp; The following information will help us get a jump start on your audit.&nbsp; You can also contact us directly if you do not have this information.&nbsp; <br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','Sustainability Scorecard','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'dallas waste management, austin waste management, commercial recycling dallas, commercial recycling austin, plastic recycling austin, plastic recycling dallas, cardboard recycling dallas, boxboard recycling austin, aluminum recycling dallas, aluminum recycling austin, plastic recycling little rock, cardboard recycling little rock, commercial recycling little rock, wood recycling little rock','Balcones Resources will perform a free resource audit for your business to jump start your Dallas, Austin or Little Rock commercial recycling program.','Balcones Resources | Dallas Waste Management, Little Rock Commercial Recycling, Austin Commercial Recycling',1),(60,'Austin','jobs-austin','','none','internal-blue','','32',710,0,'3','','Currently there are no open positions at our Austin location.&nbsp; <br><br>We are always on the lookout for good people.&nbsp; If you feel you would be a fit for Balcones Resources, <a target=\\\"\\\" title=\\\"\\\" href=\\\"mailto:careers@balconesresources.com\\\">send us</a> your resume, and we\\\'ll keep it on file for future positions.&nbsp; <br><br>Keep recycling!','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','Austin Jobs','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'Commercial Recycling Austin, Austin Recycling, SingleCycle Austin, plastic recycling austin, ecoworks austin, glass recycling austin, cardboard recycling austin<table border=\\\"0\\\" cellpadding=\\\"0\\\" cellspacing=\\\"0\\\" width=\\\"254\\\" style=\\\"border-collapse:\r\n collapse;width:254pt\\\"><colgroup><col width=\\\"254\\\" style=\\\"mso-width-source:userset;mso-width-alt:10837;width:254pt\\\"></colgroup><tbody><tr height=\\\"15\\\" style=\\\"mso-height-source:userset;height:15.0pt\\\"><td height=\\\"15\\\" class=\\\"xl100\\\" width=\\\"254\\\" style=\\\"height:15.0pt;width:254pt\\\"><br></td></tr></tbody></table>','Join our Austin recycling team for a great career and a green environment.&nbsp;','Balcones Resources | Commercial Recycling Austin, Austin Recycling, SingleCycle Austin<br>',0),(61,'Little Rock','jobs-little-rock','','none','internal-blue','','32',730,0,'3','','Currently there are no open positions at our Little Rock location.&nbsp; <br><br>We are always on the lookout for good people.&nbsp; If you feel you would be a fit for Balcones Resources, <a target=\"\" title=\"\" href=\"mailto:careers@balconesresources.com\">send us</a> your resume, and we\'ll keep it on file for future positions.&nbsp; <br><br>Keep recycling!','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','Little Rock Jobs','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'Little rock recycling, recycling little rock, cardboard recycling little rock, glass recycling little rock, commercial recycling little rock, plastic recycling little rock','Submit your resume and join the Balcones Resources Little Rock recycling team.&nbsp;','Balcones Resources | Recycling Little Rock, Jobs Little Rock, Cardboard Recycling Little Rock<br>',0),(62,'Wandering River','wandering-river','','none','internal-blue','','38',10,0,'','','<span style=\"font-style: italic;\">Acquisition allows Balcones Resources to offer customized services for small business and events</span><br><br><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">AUSTIN – October 4, 2012 –</span> Balcones Resources today announced the acquisition of Wandering River Recycling based in Austin, Texas. This cart-based service has focused on the small business and events community in and around Austin since 2008.<br><br>“Adding the expertise of Wandering River to the Balcones Resources family allows us to be the most complete recycling provider in the market,” said Kerry Getter, CEO of Balcones Resources. “When we built our new facility (opened this month) we positioned ourselves to handle all recyclables from both residential and business streams. Now we have a solution for the small business owner or property manager of multi-family residences in Austin affected by the new Universal Recycling Ordinance. It also gives us a solution for special events that need ‘one time’ recycling services such as weddings, festivals or corporate parties.”<br><br>Balcones Resources is the largest recycler in the Southwest not affiliated with a landfill. This strategic acquisition allows the company to customize services for the small business owner and event planners who want to do their part.<br><br>“I started Wandering River Recycling to fill a void in Austin’s single-stream recycling services. There were options for large business and buildings, but what would the small business or event planner do if they wanted to recycle?,” shared Bob McGivney, founder of Wandering River and new Director of Small Business Sustainability for Balcones Resources. “I built the Wandering River brand on personalized service. We started with a few friends’ businesses that we picked up with my truck, and before we knew it, the service really took off! As another Austin-born business, Balcones Resources offered the innovation and infrastructure we needed to grow the service, but the company also shared our core values of customized, personal service and sustainability.”&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>&nbsp;<br>',' <a target=\"\" title=\"\" href=\"../\">Balcones Resources</a>\r\n is the largest independent recycler and provider of comprehensive \r\nenvironmental services in the Southwest. With locations in Austin, \r\nDallas and Little Rock, the firm offers a wide range of customized \r\nenvironmental services, ranging from recycling expertise and \r\nSingleCycleTM recycling programs to alternative energy solutions, \r\ndocument destruction, equipment sales and leasing, and non-traditional \r\nrecycled products.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Media Contact:</span><br>\r\nBrooke Mayer <br>\r\n972.481.1400 x 115 <br>\r\n<a target=\"\" title=\"\" href=\"mailto:bgetter@balconesresources.com\">bgetter@balconesresources.com</a>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','Wandering River Recycling becomes part of Balcones Resources','About Balcones Resources','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'Universal Recycling Ordinance Austin, Recycling Austin, URO Austin, URO Workshops Austin, plastic recycling austin, paper recycling austin, commercial recycling austin, residential recycling austin, austin waste management, URO','Balcones Resources aquired Wondering River to help recycling Austin residents adhear to the Universal Recycling Ordinance of Austin, also known as URO Austin.','Balcones Resources | Universal Recycling Ordinance Austin, Recycling Austin, URO Austin',1),(58,'Equipment','equipment','','none','internal-green','','25',125,0,'3','','<br>','<div>Balcones Resources offers the best equipment for commercial recycling - and the expertise to design and install it according to your needs. Some of the types of recycling equipment we offer include:</div><br><ul><li>Balers</li></ul><ul><li>Compactors</li></ul><ul><li>Air systems</li></ul><ul><li>Shredders</li></ul><ul><li>Conveyor systems</li></ul><br>Don’t\r\n want the headache of choosing equipment on your own? Shift the \r\nresponsibility to Balcones’ shoulders. We offer a comprehensive, turnkey\r\n approach. Our equipment installations have been developed, \r\nmarket-tested, and perfected by our in-house experts, and used by \r\nsatisfied clients for more than 30 years.<br><br><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">Equipment Specifications</span><br>Balcones\r\n Resources is not a one-size-fits-all equipment supplier. When it’s time\r\n to place your order, we want to speak with you directly so we can be \r\nsure your commercial recycling equipment is the best possible solution for your needs.<br><br><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">Sales, Leasing &amp; Resale</span><br>All\r\n Balcones Resources equipment is available for sale or lease. We even offer resale and a range of financing programs, \r\nall designed to work for you.','<ul><li>Customization to match your operation</li></ul><ul><li>Cost/benefit analysis</li></ul><ul><li>Equipment design</li></ul><ul><li>Equipment installation</li></ul><ul><li>Sales or leasing program</li></ul><ul><li>Equipment service and preventive maintenance</li></ul><ul><li>Safety and operations training for your staff</li></ul><ul><li>Equipment operators</li></ul><ul><li>Volume monitoring and reporting</li></ul><ul><li>Excellent customer service</li></ul><br>Please <a target=\\\"\\\" title=\\\"\\\" href=\\\"/contact-us/contact-us\\\">contact us</a> to see how we can help.','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','<br>','This is How We Roll','Recycling Equipment','Benefits of Using Balcones Resources','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'&nbsp;Recycling Austin, Commercial Recycling Austin, Recycle Austin, commercial recycling austin, commercial recycling dallas, paper recycling austin, plastic recycling austin, dallas waste management, austin waste management, computer recycling austin','<div>Balcones Resources advanced equipment has made it easy for commercial companies to recycle in Austin.</div>','Balcones Resources | Recycling Austin, Commercial Recycling Austin, Recycle Austin',0),(66,'thanks','thanks','','contact','internal-purple','','',0,0,'','','<div><!-- Google Code for Online Inquiry Sent - Resources Conversion Page --></div><div><script type=\"text/javascript\"></div><div>/* <![CDATA[ */</div><div>var google_conversion_id = 983856176;</div><div>var google_conversion_language = \"en\";</div><div>var google_conversion_format = \"3\";</div><div>var google_conversion_color = \"ffffff\";</div><div>var google_conversion_label = \"CzHCCLCpqgUQsOiR1QM\";</div><div>var google_conversion_value = 0;</div><div>/* ]]> */</div><div></script></div><div><script type=\"text/javascript\" <=\"\" div=\"\"><div>src=\"http://www.googleadservices.com/pagead/conversion.js\"></div><div></script></div><div><noscript>&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div style=\"display:inline;\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;img height=\"1\" width=\"1\" style=\"border-style:none;\" alt=\"\"&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;src=\"http://www.googleadservices.com/pagead/conversion/983856176/?value=0&amp;amp;label=CzHCCLCpqgUQsOiR1Q