INSERT INTO `projects` VALUES (2,'Premier Endodontics','Premier Endodontics','premierlongisland.com','16::18::18','Premier Endodontics is one of the leading dental surgical facilities in the greater New York area','HIPPA compliant forms and a scalable CMS makes this site successful. Easy to optimize for search engines and search engine marketing.','Search Engine Marketing - Search Engine Optimization - Premier Endodontics Long Island','premier1.jpg','Secure Doctor Referral Forms','PREmierDocReferral.jpg','Hippa Compliant Patient Forms','PREmierHippa.jpg','Custom Web Development','PREmierMeetUs.jpg','','','','','','','','','','','','',2,'1'),(3,'Texas Orthopaedic Associates','Texas Orthopaedics','txorthopaedic.com','16::15::18','When an award-winning staff of sports medicine and orthopedic specialists asked us to build their website, we had to approach it with our usual design and functionality but blend it with HIPPA compliance and of course search engine optimization. ','Texas Orthopaedics had been using Word Press for years and were quite comfortable with it so utilizing our custom content management system was out. Using Word Press as the backbone for their site, we gave them the ability to add doctors, add locations, manage their blog as well as add recent news and events.\r\n','HIPPA Compliance - Custom Web Development - Content Managment System - Texas Orthopedics','txortho.jpg','Patient Assistance Center','patient-assistance-center.jpg','Search Engine Optimization','physicians-profiles.jpg','Custom Web Development','secure-patient-information-forms.jpg','','','','','','','','','','','','',4,'1'),(10,'ArkansasMatters.com','Nexstar Broadcasting','arkansasmatters.com','16::15::18','Nexstar Broadcasting\\\'s premier news website bring new meaning to the need for search engine optimization. ','Most sties are looking for search engine rankings to happen in weeks or months. Nexstar\\\'s websites required first to press, meaning top rankings for individual stories in hours. This is just one of the 32 different news websites that we created which all utilized the same content management system to create a fully interactive, up to the minute dynamic website. ','Custom Content Managment System - Custom CMS - Severe Weather Alerts and Radars','ARKmattWeather.jpg','Media Share','ARKmattMedia.jpg','Home Page','ARKmattHome2.jpg','News Page','ARKmattNews.jpg','','','','','','','','','','','','',5,''),(11,'Evo South - Custom Flash Development','Evo South','evo-south.com','15::18::16','Remember when we needed Flash to create beautiful sites like this','4W has moved on and unless someone twists our arm we don\\\'t build sites in flash anymore. 99 times out of 100 we can get the desired effects with jQuery and other JavaScript libraries. You must admit, however that evo-south.com is amazing and very functional. The custom content management system allows them to manage their flash galleries and more.','Custom Web Development - Interactive Floor Plans','flash-website-interactive-floor-plans.jpg','Interactive Flash Galleries','flash-website-interactive-galleries.jpg','Interactive Flash Gallery','flash-website-interactive-gallery.jpg','Evo South Flash Homepage','flash-website-interactive-home.jpg','','search-engine-optimization-5.jpg','','','','','','','','','','',0,'1'),(4,'Terremark a Verizon Company','Terremark','terremark.com','17::16::15::18','Terremark, a Verizon Company, needed a new website and content management system. Our team answered the call with a new theme, content and content management system upgrades.','A subsidiary of Verizon Communications Inc. (NYSE, NASDAQ:VZ), Terremark sets the standard for IT deployments with advanced infrastructure and managed service offerings that deliver the scale, security, and reliability necessary to meet the demanding requirements of enterprises and governments around the world. With a global network of data centers and a comprehensive portfolio of secure solutions, Terremark is helping enterprise and government executives realize the power and promise of the cloud today.\r\nTERREMARK AT A GLANCE\r\n<br><br>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Leader in transforming and securing enterprise-class IT on a global scale</li>\r\n<li>Data centers in North America, Latin America, Europe and the Asia-Pacific region</li>\r\n<li>Passed SAS-70 Type II Audit</li>\r\n<li>Microsoft Gold Certified Partner</li>\r\n<li>United States General Services Administration (GSA) Schedule# GS35F0073U</li>\r\n</ul>','Custom Web Development - Global Data Centers','terremark.jpg','Search Engine Marketing - Data Security','custom-web-development-2.jpg','Search Engine Optimiisation - Multi Language Site','search-engine-optimization-3.jpg','Search Engine Marketing, Federal Goverment','search-engine-marketing-4.jpg','','content-managment-systems-5.jpg','','','','','','','','','','',1,'1'),(5,'Project','Project','projectpdx.com','15::18','As we stated before, at W4 we believe flash websites are a thing of the past, however the customer gets what they want, so working on this website allowed us to sharpen our skills and bring our capabilities to a new level.','Our team specializes in creating beautiful, functional and appealing websites without the use of flash. With mobile devices growing in popularity and tablet usage on the rise we feel that it is important not to miss out on the customers on the move.','Custom Web Development - Project Home Page','project.jpg','Custom Flash Development - Building Gallery Timeline','custom-flash-development2.jpg','Flash Website Gallery','flash-gallery.jpg','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',3,''),(12,'BullionExpress.com','NTRMetals','bullionexpress.com','15::16','The backbone of this site is a content management system written by us, from scratch.','BullionExpress.com is a perfect example that a highly search engine optimized site can be beautiful and highly dynamic. The collapsible dashboard displays up to the moment prices for gold silver and platinum as well as history data going back as far as five years.','Search Engine Optimization','bullionExpress.jpg','Search Engine Marketing, Content Management System','bullion-express2.jpg','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',6,'1'),(13,'Headwaters MB','Headwaters MB','headwatersmb.com','15::16::18','Experts at serving Middle-Market Businesses, Business-Owning Families and Family Offices.','The designers had fun with this site. With over 20 different layouts and custom illustrations for each this site goes deep. The content management system used here was written from scratch to allow the client full control over their site. They can add pages, position pages on one of three different navigation areas, create new content and upload images.\r\n','SEO','headwaters1.jpg','SEM','headwaters2.jpg','Custom Web Development','headwaters3.jpg','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',7,'1'),(14,'NIIT','NIIT','www.niit.us/content/impact','15::16','NIIT training is their business.','This micro-site is built completely within the clients CRM, Eloqua. The parallax scrolling adds a flare to to a site that is highly search engine optimized.','CRM Integration','niit1.jpg','Micro Site','niit2.jpg','Eloqua Content Integration','niit3.jpg','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',8,'1'),(15,'Balcones Shred','Balcones Shred','balconesshred.com','15::17::16::18','Balcones Shred  is one of Dallas\\\'s largest document destruction companies.','Balconesshred.com is a perfect mix of  appearance and  functionality while still being highly optimized for both search engine marketing and search engine optimization. Their content management system allows for fresh content, videos and graphics throughout the site.','Search Engine Optimization','balconesShred1.jpg','Search Engine Marketing','balconesShred2.jpg','Custom Content Managment System','balconesShred3.jpg','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',9,'1');
